2.01    2009-03-03      Bugfix: Q< and Q> now work on pre- perl 5.10;
                        64-bit support now works on 32-bit machines, and
                          < and > work on pre- perl 5.10.0 (this is because
                          to implement the Q>/Q< fix, I needed to emulate
                          pack() so am no longer bound by its limitations)
                         
